== reverso

Interface for reverso.net translation service.

Includes command-line tool named _reverso_.


== Usage

  require 'rubygems'
  require 'reverso'
  Reverso::Translator.translate('The love', :from => 'En', :to => 'German')


== Requirements

* json (tested with json-1.5.1 gem)


== Install

  gem install reverso


